      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FATE AWAITS (2) was one of the leading three-year-olds of last season and ended his campaign with a trip across the Tasman to place in the rich The Velocity in November. Won the Group 1 Rising Sun here earlier in the year. Goes straight to the 2647m and a standing start first up but has won three of four fresh attempts and has plenty of class. STRIKEM NZ (1) drew on the back row and was held up when midfield last time but had recorded a win and a placing in his previous two outings. Suited up to a distance where he has won both attempts. TARGARYEN NZ (4) could be close to a win having come from this mark to place in his last three outings here. ARKIN WICKED (3) has been solid in two starts from this mark since a win here and he is proven at this longer distance.",
